            <div class='post' itemprop='text'>
              <p>FYI.<br>
This was implemented via <a href="https://github.com/getredash/redash/pull/5159" class="inline-onebox" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Expire sessions after 6 hours of inactivity by rauchy Â· Pull Request #5159 Â· getredash/redash Â· GitHub</a> <img src="https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/twitter/rocket.png?v=12" title=":rocket:" class="emoji" alt=":rocket:" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20"><br>
Set the environment variable <code>SESSION_EXPIRY_TIME</code> to your liking. (The default is 60 * 60 * 6 (6 hours)</p>
            </div>

